{
  "texts": [
    "We divided the heldout dataset into two splits: parameter estimation (33%) and test (66%).",
    "Using the parameter estimation set, we computed the centroid of all sequences corresponding to a given species.",
    "At the test stage, we assigned a sequence to a species according to the centroid with the smallest L2 distance.",
    "Property prediction.",
    "We tested the models using fivefold crossvalidation."
  ]
}